    <item>
      <title>随着原油价格下跌，石油巨头必须借钱来偿还投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/as-crude-fades-big-oil-must-borrow-to-pay-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[原油价格和炼油利润率的下降可能会迫使五大超级石油公司中的四家借钱来资助最近一个季度的150亿美元股票回购，这引发了人们对这些派息的长期可持续性的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/as-crude-fades-big-oil-must-borrow-to-pay-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键一周伊始，股市上涨，油价下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对伊朗的报复性打击避开了石油设施后，市场弥漫着一种宽慰的感觉，原油价格在本周初暴跌，美国股指期货上涨，这对投资者来说将是一个关键的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
